DataSourcePortable.Content:
<DataSourceDefinition> <FromSql Alias="A" SelectCommand="SELECT A.HANDLE,
 A.HANDLE CHAVE,
 A.CONTATESOURARIA,
 B.NOME,
 A.OPERACAO,
 D.SIGLA,
 A.DOCUMENTO,
 A.DATAEMISSAO,
 A.HISTORICO,
 B.NUMEROCONTA,
 B.DIGITOVERIFICADOR,
 A.NUMEROCHEQUE,
 A.CONCILIADO,
 E.DATAEMISSAO DATAEXTRATO
 FROM FN_CONTASTESOURARIA B,
 GN_OPERACOES C,
 FN_TIPOSDOCUMENTOS D,
 TS_LANCAMENTOS A LEFT JOIN TS_EXTRATOBANCARIO E ON E.CONCILIACAO = A.CONCILIACAO
 WHERE B.HANDLE = A.CONTATESOURARIA
 AND
 (
 C.HANDLE = A.OPERACAO
 AND D.HANDLE = C.TIPODOCUMENTO
 )" /> <Fields> <Field Alias="HANDLE" From="A" Path="HANDLE" /> <Field Alias="CHAVE" From="A" Path="CHAVE" /> <Field Alias="CONTATESOURARIA" From="A" Path="CONTATESOURARIA" /> <Field Alias="NOME" From="A" Path="NOME" /> <Field Alias="OPERACAO" From="A" Path="OPERACAO" /> <Field Alias="SIGLA" From="A" Path="SIGLA" /> <Field Alias="DOCUMENTO" From="A" Path="DOCUMENTO" /> <Field Alias="DATAEMISSAO" From="A" Path="DATAEMISSAO" /> <Field Alias="HISTORICO" From="A" Path="HISTORICO" /> <Field Alias="NUMEROCONTA" From="A" Path="NUMEROCONTA" /> <Field Alias="DIGITOVERIFICADOR" From="A" Path="DIGITOVERIFICADOR" /> <Field Alias="NUMEROCHEQUE" From="A" Path="NUMEROCHEQUE" /> <Field Alias="CONCILIADO" From="A" Path="CONCILIADO" /> <Field Alias="DATAEXTRATO" From="A" Path="DATAEXTRATO" /> </Fields> </DataSourceDefinition>
